appear here automatically with full\n        <strong>TopCasinoScout (TCS) scores</strong>.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- INLINE STYLES FOR THIS PAGE -->\n    <style>\n      .tcs-section-grid {\n        display:grid;\n        grid-template-columns:minmax(0,1.6fr) minmax(0,1.1fr);\n        gap:30px;\n        margin-top:30px;\n      }\n      .tcs-block {\n        background:#080826;\n        border-radius:18px;\n        border:1px solid #241e67;\n        padding:24px 22px 22px;\n        box-shadow:0 0 24px rgba(0,0,0,.45);\n        margin-bottom:24px;\n      }\n      .tcs-block h2 {\n        margin:0 0 12px;\n        font-size:1.3rem;\n        color:#ffcc33;\n      }\n      .tcs-block h3 {\n        margin:0 0 8px;\n        font-size:1.02rem;\n        color:#ffea9c;\n      }\n      .tcs-block p {\n        margin:0 0 10px;\n        font-size:.95rem;\n        line-height:1.7;\n        color:#d5e0ff;\n      }\n      .tcs-block ul {\n        margin:0 0 6px;\n        padding-left:18px;\n        font-size:.95rem;\n        line-height:1.7;\n        color:#d5e0ff;\n      }\n      .tcs-label-pill {\n        display:inline-block;\n        padding:4px 10px;\n        border-radius:999px;\n        background:#140f3f;\n        border:1px solid #38318c;\n        font-size:.75rem;\n        letter-spacing:.1em;\n        text-transform:uppercase;\n        color:#a8c7ff;\n        margin-bottom:10px;\n      }\n      .tcs-tagline {\n        font-size:.82rem;\n        color:#8fa1ff;\n        margin-top:4px;\n      }\n\n      .tcs-coming-grid {\n        display:grid;\n        grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(260px,1fr));\n        gap:22px;\n        margin-top:18px;\n      }\n      .tcs-coming-card {\n        background:#080826;\n        border-radius:16px;\n        border:1px dashed #3b348f;\n        padding:18px 18px 16px;\n        box-shadow:0 0 18px rgba(0,0,0,.4);\n      }\n      .tcs-coming-card h3 {\n        margin:0 0 6px;\n        font-size:1rem;\n        color:#ffcc33;\n      }\n      .tcs-coming-card p {\n        margin:0;\n        font-size:.9rem;\n        color:#c9d4ff;\n        line-height:1.6;\n      }\n\n      .tcs-btn-primary,\n      .tcs-btn-secondary {\n        display:inline-flex;\n        align-items:center;\n        justify-content:center;\n        padding:10px 22px;\n        border-radius:999px;\n        font-weight:700;\n        font-size:.92rem;\n        text-decoration:none;\n        transition:.2s ease;\n        white-space:nowrap;\n      }\n      .tcs-btn-primary {\n        background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ff9a1f,#ffcc33);\n        color:#1a1038;\n        border:none;\n        box-shadow:0 0 16px rgba(255,204,51,.45);\n      }\n      .tcs-btn-primary:hover {\n        transform:translateY(-1px);\n        box-shadow:0 0 22px rgba(255,204,51,.7);\n      }\n      .tcs-btn-secondary {\n        border:1px solid #ffcc33;\n        color:#ffcc33;\n        background:transparent;\n      }\n      .tcs-btn-secondary:hover {\n        background:rgba(255,204,51,.08);\n        box-shadow:0 0 16px rgba(255,204,51,.45);\n      }\n\n      @media (max-width: 900px) {\n        .tcs-section-grid {\n          grid-template-columns:1fr;\n        }\n      }\n    </style>\n\n    <!-- MAIN CONTENT GRID -->\n    <div class=\"tcs-section-grid\">\n\n      <!-- LEFT COLUMN -->\n      <div>\n\n        <!-- WHAT ARE FREE SPIN SLOTS -->\n        <div class=\"tcs-block\">\n          <span class=\"tcs-label-pill\">Guide</span>\n          <h2>What Are Free Spin Slots?</h2>\n          <p>\n            <strong>Free spin slots</strong> are online slot games where the casino gives you a batch of\n            free spins instead of (or in addition to) a standard cash match bonus. You spin the reels\n            for free, and any winnings are usually converted into bonus money with wagering attached.\n          </p>\n          <p>\n            Casinos use free spins as part of:\n          </p>\n          <ul>\n            <li><strong>No-deposit free spins</strong> for new sign-ups (rare, high value, strict terms).</li>\n            <li><strong>First deposit packages</strong> (e.g., 100% up to $500 + 100 free spins on a featured slot).</li>\n            <li><strong>Reload offers</strong> for existing players, especially on weekends and new games.</li>\n          </ul>\n          <p class=\"tcs-tagline\">\n            Our goal is to highlight the <strong>best free spins deals</strong> where the terms are realistic\n            and the slot selection is worth your time.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- HOW WE WILL RANK THEM -->\n        <div class=\"tcs-block\">\n          <span class=\"tcs-label-pill\">How We Rate</span>\n          <h2>How We Will Rank Free Spin Casinos</h2>\n          <p>\n            Once we start listing <strong>free spins casinos</strong> on this page, each brand will receive\n            a full <strong>TopCasinoScout Score (TCS)</strong> on our 0\u201310,000 scale. For free spin slots,\n            we pay special attention to:\n          </p>\n          <ul>\n            <li><strong>Number of free spins</strong> vs. minimum deposit required.</li>\n            <li><strong>Wagering requirements</strong> on winnings from free spins.</li>\n            <li><strong>Game weighting</strong> \u2013 which slots the spins can actually be used on.</li>\n            <li><strong>Max win caps</strong> and cashout limitations for free spin rewards.</li>\n            <li><strong>Payout speed</strong> and reputation of the casino itself.</li>\n          </ul>\n          <p>\n            If a casino advertises huge \u201cfree\u201d spin packages with impossible terms, low max wins or\n            confusing restrictions, it won\u2019t make our recommended list.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- RIGHT COLUMN -->\n      <div>\n\n        <!-- COMING SOON GRID -->\n        <div class=\"tcs-block\">\n          <span class=\"tcs-label-pill\">Coming Soon</span>\n          <h2>Upcoming Free Spin Slot Deals</h2>\n          <p>\n            Our team is currently shortlisting casinos that can offer <strong>transparent free spin bonuses</strong>.\n            We\u2019re also in talks to secure at least one <strong>exclusive free spins package</strong> for TCS readers.\n          </p>\n\n          <div class=\"tcs-coming-grid\">\n            <div class=\"tcs-coming-card\">\n              <h3>Exclusive Free Spin Partner #1</h3>\n              <p>\n                Negotiation in progress for a welcome package featuring a strong block of free spins on a\n                top-tier slot. TCS scoring &amp; full review will appear here once confirmed.\n              </p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"tcs-coming-card\">\n              <h3>Low-Wagering Free Spins</h3>\n              <p>\n                We\u2019re prioritising casinos with realistic wagering (or low-wagering) on free spin winnings,\n                not just flashy headline numbers.\n              </p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"tcs-coming-card\">\n              <h3>No-Deposit Free Spins</h3>\n              <p>\n                True <strong>no-deposit free spins casinos</strong> are rare and often geo-restricted. If we find\n                a trustworthy option, it will be highlighted here with clear country availability.\n              </p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          <p class=\"tcs-tagline\">\n            Bookmark this page or check back after major launches \u2013 free spin offers change frequently.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- INTERNAL NAVIGATION -->\n        <div class=\"tcs-block\">\n          <span class=\"tcs-label-pill\">Next Steps</span>\n          <h2>Where to Go While You Wait</h2>\n          <p>\n            While we finalise our list of <strong>free spin slots casinos</strong>, you can still find excellent\n            value in our other bonus hubs and detailed reviews:\n          </p>\n          <ul>\n            <li>\n              Compare high-value welcome offers on our\n              <a href=\"/top-casino-bonuses\" style=\"color:#ffcc33; text-decoration:none;\">Top Casino Bonuses</a> page.\n            </li>\n            <li>\n              Watch for special sign-up rewards on the\n              <a href=\"/no-deposit-bonuses\" style=\"color:#ffcc33; text-decoration:none;\">No Deposit Bonuses</a> hub.\n            </li>\n            <li>\n              Read honest, long-form reviews in our\n              <a href=\"/casino-reviews\" style=\"color:#ffcc33; text-decoration:none;\">Casino Reviews</a> section.\n            </li>\n            <li>\n              Check for enhanced welcome deals using our\n              <a href=\"/casino-promo-codes\" style=\"color:#ffcc33; text-decoration:none;\">Casino Promo Codes</a>.\n            </li>\n          </ul>\n\n          <div style=\"margin-top:12px; display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:10px;\">\n            <a href=\"/top-casino-bonuses\" class=\"tcs-btn-primary\">View Top Casino Bonuses</a>\n            <a href=\"/casino-rankings\" class=\"tcs-btn-secondary\">See Global Rankings</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</section>";
